    "description": {
      "short": "A magnificent longsword wreathed in eternal flames",
      "full": "This legendary blade was forged in the heart of a dying star by the ancient smith Thalgrim. Its blade burns with an eternal flame that never dims, and it is said to have been wielded by heroes in battles against darkness itself.",
      "appearance": "The blade appears to be made of pure golden metal that pulses with inner fire. Flames dance along its edge without consuming it. The crossguard is shaped like phoenix wings, and the pommel holds a ruby that glows like an ember."
    }
  },
