  "narrative": {
    "background": "Flamebrand was forged by the legendary smith Thalgrim at the request of the Sun God Aurion. It was created to combat the forces of darkness during the Age of Shadows, and has been passed down through generations of heroes. The blade is sentient and chooses its own wielders, refusing to serve those with dark hearts.",
    "personality": "The sword has a proud and noble personality. It communicates through feelings and impressions rather than words, guiding its wielder toward acts of heroism and justice.",
